cs.RO, cs.HC, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper discusses the development of an AR interaction system for navigating and supporting human workers in autonomous warehouses. This involves robotics (cs.RO) as well as human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computer vision (cs.CV) for the AR modalities. The improved planner mentioned in the abstract also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the safety-critical aspect of the project suggests the involvement of systems and control (cs.SY).
